<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.5.6">
<l>kaṉṟap paṟaikaṟaṅkak kaṇṭavartaṅ kaṇkaḷippa</l>
<l>maṉṟil marakkālkūt tāṭiṉāṉ kāṇēṭī</l>
<l>maṉṟil marakkālkūt tāṭiṉā ṉākilum</l>
<l>eṉṟu mariya ṉimaiyōrkkum cāḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, Friend! As the drums thundered so that [the drummers] ached</l>
<l rend="indent">and as onlookers’ eyes reeled,</l>
<l>He performed the stilt dance in the public square.</l>
<l>Although he performed the stilt dance in the public square,</l>
<l>He is always a rarity for even the unblinking [celestials]. Cāḻalē!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
